---
// Gear
---

<section id="gear">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label">Gear</p>
    <h2>What I bring</h2>

    <div class="gear-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>vMix workstation</h3>
        <span class="pill">Production rig</span>
        <ul>
          <li>Intel i9-12900K</li>
          <li>NVIDIA RTX 3080Ti</li>
          <li>32GB RAM</li>
          <li>Windows (vMix native)</li>
          <li>Home studio / remote production</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="gear-note">
          Purpose-built for live show switching, graphics integration, and
          multi-caller remote production at 1080p60 with records.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Field kit</h3>
        <span class="pill">Fly-pack essentials</span>
        <ul>
          <li>SDI barrels &amp; adapters</li>
          <li>USB drives (multiple)</li>
          <li>Assorted cables</li>
          <li>Box cutters, pens, pencils</li>
          <li>Show-day necessities (6 years refined)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="gear-note">
          Assembled over six years of on-site work. Everything that's saved
          a show at some point is in this bag.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>MacBook</h3>
        <span class="pill">Mobile</span>
        <ul>
          <li>Remote access &amp; monitoring</li>
          <li>Light production tasks</li>
          <li>Travels to every show</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  h2 { margin-bottom: 2rem; }

  .gear-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .card .pill { margin-bottom: 1rem; display: inline-block; }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  ul li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  ul li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent-alt);
  }

  .gear-note {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
